      <body>
         <div type="abstract" resp="kg">
            <p>
               <rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3609"><rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs
                        type="person" ref="pe__johann_koll_SB_CD_01565">Hanns Ko/ell, <roleName
                           type="occ" corresp="org__wien-st_stephan">korherr</roleName> zu sand
                        Stephan zu Wienn, <roleName type="occ"
                           corresp="org__wien-st_philipp_und_st_jakob_kapelle-altar_st_maria"
                           >capplan</roleName> Unser Lieben Frauen altars, gelegen in der abseiten
                        sand Philipps und sand Jacobs cappellen in Kollnerhof daselbs</rs>,</rs>
                  <triggerstring n="disp">gibt <add>gelts purkrechts</add></triggerstring>
                  <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="person"
                        ref="pe__johann_fuerst_QGW_II_II_3609">Hannsen dem Fürsten, dem <roleName
                           type="prof">slosser</roleName>, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">burger</roleName> ze Wienn</rs>, und <rs
                        type="person" ref="pe__dorothea_QGW_II_II_3609">Dorothen, seiner <roleName
                           type="kin" corresp="pe__johann_fuerst_QGW_II_II_3609"
                           >hausfraun</roleName></rs>,</rs>
                  <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_II"><measure>1 lb dn.</measure>
                     <triggerstring n="fn">gelts purkrechts</triggerstring> von <rs type="place"
                        ref="pl__wien-immo_schlossergasse_5"><roleName type="owner"
                           corresp="pe__johann_fuerst_QGW_II_II_3609">ihrem</roleName>
                        <rs type="person" ref="pe__dorothea_QGW_II_II_3609"><add>ihrem</add></rs>
                        Hause, <roleName type="topo" corresp="pl__wien-schlossergasse">gelegen
                           undern Slossern zu Wienn</roleName>
                        <roleName type="topo" corresp="pl__wien-immo_alter_rossmarkt_5"
                           >hinder</roleName>
                        <rs type="place" ref="pl__wien-immo_alter_rossmarkt_5">der padstuben
                              <roleName type="topo" corresp="pl__wien-alter_rossmarkt">am Alten
                              Rossmarkt</roleName></rs></rs>,</rs>
                  <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_I">um <measure>8 lb dn.</measure>
                     abzulösen.</rs></rs>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div type="seal">
            <p><rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3609">Siegler: <rs type="person"
                     ref="pe__ulrich_gundloch_QGW_II_II_3454">Ulreich der Gundloch, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">burger</roleName> zu Wienn, als
                        <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien-st_philipp_und_st_jakob_kapelle-altar_st_maria"
                        >Lehensherr</roleName> des Altars</rs> und <rs type="person"
                     ref="pe__arnold_gallander_QGW_II_III_3864">Arnolt Gallander, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">burger</roleName></rs>.</rs>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div type="nota">
            <p>Indorsate: a) Kiczinger, slosser, haus undern Slossern, b) ablosbrief ex parte
               Kiczinger haus [ under] den Slossern. </p>
         </div>
